__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  Update:
    properties:
      stream: optional<boolean>
      message: string
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

status.yml.rawContents:
imports:
  root: __package__.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    update:
      path: /status
      method: POST
      auth: false
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: root.Update
        content-type: application/json
      examples:
        - headers:
            X-API-Key: '[object Object]'
          request:
            message: message
      retries:
        disabled: true
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

status2.yml.rawContents:
imports:
  root: __package__.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    update:
      path: /status2
      method: POST
      auth: false
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: root.Update
        content-type: application/json
      examples:
        - headers:
            X-API-Key: '[object Object]'
          request:
            message: message
      audiences:
        - private
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Test extension `x-fern-retries`.
version:
  header: X-API-Version
  default: 2.0.0
  values:
    - 1.0.0
    - 2.0.0
    - Latest
auth-schemes:
  BearerAuthScheme:
    scheme: bearer
auth: BearerAuthScheme
headers:
  X-API-Key:
    type: string
    name: apiKey
